    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 18th level, your have become a True Ruler of the Ocean. As an Action in your turn, you can pay 30 Chakra. You flood the area around you in water, cresting a massive Lake of Water in a 120ft circle around you, and 60ft deep. As part of the same Action, You cast the <em>Summoning Jutsu</em> at S-Rank, using the Stat Block of any choice found in the Jutsu Book with Access to the <em>Water Release</em> Keyword.</p>",
